data.description: INCREDIBLE GOLF FRONT 5/4 POOL HOME IN SORRENTO'S PREMIER GATED GOLF COMMUNITY - If you've been looking for an immaculate, move-in ready home with all of the amenities on a cul-de-sac street, look no further. Red Tail is a highly desirable guard-gated golf community. Home features/upgrades include: granite in all baths with bronze fixtures and accents; gorgeous engineered wood flooring in public rooms, tile in wet areas; custom stacked stone accent walls, gas fireplace in family room; coffered foyer and dining room ceilings; master suite with recessed ceiling; crown moulding and custom millwork, custom blinds, spacious kitchen w/ fabulous backsplash, gas cooktop, wall oven, and granite-island. The owners' suite includes a huge walk-in closet, a large shower, a garden tub, and dual sinks. Screened lanai, french doors with an outdoor pool oasis complete with tranquil waterfall and a heated spa with a fountain. Delightful outdoor covered bar area for entertaining complete with a custom firepit for cool nights. Plenty of natural light and high ceiling offer an open and airy feel. Fully fenced yard with an unobstructed view of the golf course. Over-sized three-car garage; tile roof with gutters and paver drive. This home shows great attention to detail and design. Just minutes from the quaint shops & dining of the charming village of Mt. Dora to the west and the upscale restaurants and nightlife of Lake Mary to the east; now with the Wekiva Parkway outside the back gate, Downtown & the Int’l Airports are just minutes away. Let’s not forget to mention the Outstanding Amenities that Redtail has to offer, including Golf, Fitness room, Tennis, a Clubhouse with a Restaurant and Bar, a Pool, and over 400 acres of Stunning Views And don't forget, the entire back of the home opens to sweeping golf course views!  Come enjoy the very best Central Florida has to offer.
